title: Thompson Announces Constituent Staff Hours in Huntingdon (Glenn W Thompson)
text: ( Source : Glenn W Thompson ) Washington, DC - Congressman Glenn 'GT' Thompson ( PA-05 ) today announced that his staff will hold constituent office hours in Huntingdon on Tuesday, Oct. 27. Thompson's staff will be available to answer questions
